      • updatePaymentMethod

        public void updatePaymentMethod(PaymentMethod paymentMethod)
                         throws ProtectPayException
        Updated a payment method. While this method accepts a payment method as an argument, not all the fields are available to be updated. The following fields are not available for updates: accountCountryCode, accountNumber, bankNumber and type (if credit card).
        Parameters:
        paymentMethod - the payment method to update
        Throws:
        ProtectPayException - if the request fails
